Date of Birth: August, 21, 1809<br/>
Birthplace: near Big Bone, Kentucky, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle: February 12, 1849<br/>
Death: November 17, 1883<br/>
<br/>
Born Aug. 21, 1809, near Big Bone, Boone Co., Kentucky, to Joseph Rich and Nancy O'Neal. Ordained apostle Feb. 12, 1849, by Brigham Young, at Salt Lake City, Utah, at age 39; died Nov. 17, 1883, at Paris, Bear Lake Co., Idaho, at age 74.